@startuml
title Skava Integration – Order Replaced Completed

participant "Skava AWS" as skawa {
  participant "Skava Event\nOrchestration" as seo1
}

database "Legacy DB" as ldb1

rectangle Kafka #LightBlue250-#White/70%{
    rectangle Topics <<queue>> 
}


seo1 ->>Topics : <b><color:black>1</color></b>\nProduce OrderReplacedCompleted Message 

==<font color=black>**Async**</font> ==



Kafka->YL Services:<b><color:black>2</color></b>\nConsume OrderReplacedCompleted Message 


activate YL Services::Order Sync Service  
YL Services ::Order Sync Service -->ldb1:3 Update order status in legacy db   
deactivate YL Services::Order Sync Service  

return **4 Response/**\n<b><u>Order ID </u></b>  


YLServices-->kafka:**5 Produce OrderReplacedCompletedProcessed Message**   

==<font color=black>**Async**</font> ==




skawa <- kafka :**6 Consume OrderReplacedCompletedProcessed Message**  





@enduml
